name: Preist Pack (Mitre hats and church backgrounds)
description:
Forgive me father for I have sinned.
This is a model that's based on the the mitre the rectangular hat of a priest as well as some training on church interiors, and exteriors. Tends to work best at 0.6. This model was trained on NAI anime-full-pruned and generated in Anything5. Made with the Kohya tool for AI Training through google colab. Any suggestions to improve or recommended things for the data set would be appreciated.

modelVersions.description: This was trained on a variety of real and anime mitre (yes some pictures of the actual pope are in the mix).
